last_episode_to_air.name: Attack of the Conscience
last_episode_to_air.overview: Captain Phasma gives Finn the chance to become a full-fledged Stormtrooper. Finn initially accepts - but then has second thoughts.

name: LEGO Star Wars : The Resistance Rises
original_name: LEGO Star Wars : The Resistance Rises
overview: A series of animated shorts that take place prior to the First Order's attack on Jakku and tell never-before-told stories including Kylo Ren, Han Solo, Finn, Rey, BB-8, Maz Kanata and more.

episodes.name: Poe to the Rescue
episodes.overview: With the help of C-3PO and BB-8, pilot Poe Dameron devises a plan to rescue of one of the Resistance’s most important leaders, Admiral Ackbar, from Kylo Ren and Captain Phasma.

episodes.name: The Trouble with Rathtars
episodes.overview: Han Solo and Chewbacca have their hands full with a pack of misbehaving Rathtars as they attempt to transport their carnivorous cargo to a rendezvous with Bala Tik, the pirate. Things go from bad to worse when First Order TIE Fighters pull the freighter over, forcing Han to think quickly and somehow save his skin from both the First Order and the rampaging creatures.

episodes.name: Hunting for Han
episodes.overview: At the castle of pirate Maz Kanata (the gathering spot for A-list Scum and Villainy across the galaxy), Maz prepares to trade with scurvy pirate Bala Tik. Bala Tik’s demands that Maz reveal the location of Han Solo, whom Bala Tik accuses of cheating him out of his Rathtars. As it happens, every unsavory character there has a beef with Han, and soon the Han-haters erupt in a brawl that stops when a mysterious old coot sends the angry Scum on a wild goose chase after Han.

episodes.name: Rey Strikes Back
episodes.overview: On remote Jakku, Rey strives to make ends meet by scavenging ruined Star Destroyers, but the heartless trader Unkar Plutt isn’t making it easy for her. Angry at what he perceives as Rey’s ingratitude, Plutt sends henchmen to steal her cherished Tank Speeder. The two not-so-bright baddies meet their match in the determined Rey, who stops at nothing to get her beloved “Bumper” back.

episodes.name: Attack of the Conscience
episodes.overview: Captain Phasma gives Finn the chance to become a full-fledged Stormtrooper. Finn initially accepts - but then has second thoughts.
